{"tid":442212,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"做 IT 的應如何看科技產業, 地球村化, 資訊科技革命 ?!","createTime":"2017-10-20T11:44:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T11:33:47.000Z","uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f0fabb41b2940bf85c1d977f3bac5b0e87519fb9","tid":442212,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T11:44:09.000Z","msg":"IT 好多人基本看, 是一份工.<br />\n都岩, 因世上大部份是打工仔,<br />\n打工仔睇的, 都是基本自身的, 貼身的環境.<br />\n<br />\n但有份工, 都需要有公司開, 去請人, 才有這份工的空缺, 及對這員工持續需要.<br />\n那就, 可試將著眼點, 看IT企業.<br />\n而, 短短的看過去這3-5 年, 港美經濟都不錯, 而IT 工都比一般工都更搶人,<br />\n而價亦高了, 也仍難請人.<br />\n<br />\n那就, 可再嘗試將視野, 看IT 產業, 科技產業, 看看到底發生什麼事.......<br />\n<br />\n而, 都多次提及, 地球十大企業, 頭3 大都是 IT 公司,<br />\n頭廿大企業, 都有7-8 間都是 IT 企業.&nbsp;<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_public_corporations_by_market_capitalization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FList_of_public_corporations_by_market_capitalization&d=rNlrB5lgYtay0WU3ziUhL%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=2355691e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_public_corporations_by_market_capitalization</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://dogsofthedow.com/largest-companies-by-market-cap.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdogsofthedow.com%2Flargest-companies-by-market-cap.htm&d=rNlrB5lgYtay0WU3ziUhL%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=c17bbc90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://dogsofthedow.com/largest-companies-by-market-cap.htm</a><br />\n那就要細心想一想, IT 對地球做出了如何的影響........<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾多次提及, 地球在資訊科技革命化. (出處源於1997年比爾蓋茨的擁抱未來).<br />\n都需要嘗試去理解, 再去把握, 深化, 創富......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都是拋磚引玉, 班門弄斧,<br />\n各位大哥指教一下..............................<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a49d45a6237c8e5419551450d7b87cfd6186e989","tid":442212,"uid":5496,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T11:55:15.000Z","msg":"屌你 自己做功課做project做essay就自己諗啦<br />\n用人個腦唔洗腦<br />\non99"},{"pid":"b7d82eaf92b198e00c38019fc3863a59447a7a3b","tid":442212,"uid":5496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T11:55:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你 自己做功課做project做essay就自己諗啦<br />\n用人個腦唔洗腦<br />\non99</blockquote><br />\n 錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab66f9e7829654c48b5ed938a210cd62f1bf8022","tid":442212,"uid":61249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T13:54:31.000Z","msg":"科技應該屬於大眾，不應只被少數人掌握"},{"pid":"7d1db28ef9e03e7b3d5d1679008578ee449d7e85","tid":442212,"uid":38316,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T02:19:54.000Z","msg":"而家好多一級既公司<br />\n雖然俾外界定義為科技公司<br />\n但係佢哋只係用科技只係一個橋樑嚟做生意<br />\n除咗線上服務之外佢哋都有好多嘢要兼顧<br />\n好似亞馬遜，gogoVan咁<br />\n但你唔會叫商務同其他Call台做IT公司<br />\n<br />\n如果將運用IT既公司叫晒做IT公司<br />\n我諗根據而家既定義<br />\n十年八載可能頭 100既公司都叫做IT公司<br />\n<br />\n正如Development ＝IT Support一樣成日俾人攞出嚟笑既情況"},{"pid":"acfcee450dee4942653e0d5a28b6135d49dc24e1","tid":442212,"uid":105553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T02:23:43.000Z","msg":"亞J大由鄉土玩到嚟連登。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ae0d157258ec606e04f930c2f18822b662bdcf","tid":442212,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T02:25:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家好多一級既公司<br />\n雖然俾外界定義為科技公司<br />\n但係佢哋只係用科技<span style=\"color: red;\">作為</span>一個橋樑嚟做生意<br />\n除咗線上服務之外佢哋都有好多嘢要兼顧<br />\n好似亞馬遜，gogoVan咁<br />\n但你唔會叫商務同其他Call台做IT公司<br />\n<br />\n如果將運用IT既公司叫晒做IT公司<br />\n我諗根據而家既定義<br />\n十年八載可能頭 100既公司都叫做IT公司<br />\n<br />\n正如Development ＝IT Support一樣成日俾人攞出嚟笑既情況</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7dc1550c337af6f6b6786aac19076d6420db8ea6","tid":442212,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T05:41:51.000Z","msg":"open source"},{"pid":"125f0eb90c1b3608b18e940648f912bb86bb9c6b","tid":442212,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor